| Documentation | Sonnet | Standard |

---

## Key Learnings

- The best model depends on the task.
- More reasoning effort usually means better analysis.
- Giving proper context improves results significantly.
- Sonnet is a great balance between speed and intelligence.
- AI tools become more useful when used strategically.

---

## Conclusion

The biggest lesson from Day 7 was that using AI effectively is not only about writing good prompts. 
Choosing the right model and reasoning level can make a huge difference in the quality of results.

